joxy

Class JoxyLookAndFeel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.LookAndFeel
      • javax.swing.plaf.basic.BasicLookAndFeel
        • joxy.JoxyLookAndFeel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class JoxyLookAndFeel
extends BasicLookAndFeel
    This class is the main class of the Joxy Look and Feel. It extends the Basic look and feel.

    Besides implementing the obligatory (abstract) methods, this class also provides a getVersion() method, that can be used to get the version identifier (e.g. "0.2.0") of this version of Joxy.

    Author:
    Thom Castermans, Willem Sonke
